'''line_reverse_mode''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets whether trains are disallowed to reverse at stations.<br><br>
true = trains can reverse at end of line only<br>
false = trains can reverse either at end of line and at stations<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
line_reverse_mode = false
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ true | false ]

'''Default:''' false


